item.title: Triple H/ Vince and other WWE wrestlers celebrate Triple H's birthday!
item.description:
Triple H/ Vince and other WWE wrestlers celebrate Triple H's birthday!
After Raw went off air here in DC, we had a dark match that followed with a suprise for Triple H that included his father-in-law Vince McMahon and many other WWE wrestlers. Batista made a suprise appearance and boy was there a lot of cake being thrown around. Hunter tried to escape but Vince threatened to sing if he didn't return. The Raw roster came out, and Vince McMahon sang happy birthday to his son-in-law. Someone got him with the cake before he came back out. He said thanks, then everyone around the ring tossed cakes on Hunter. Then Batista came out, and Vince and Show held Hunter for Dave to pie Hunter in the face, but he ducked and Show got it. Vince came back to pie Big Show, and they tossed cake as well. hope you enjoy!
